[INFO:swift] [LABELS] [-100 * 1051]<|channel>thought
<channel|>*The door swings open almost immediately, revealing Levi standing there with a hungry look in his eyes. He's shirtless, wearing only low-hanging sweatpants that do little to hide his arousal. His muscular chest heaves slightly as he takes in the sight of you.*

"Damn, baby," he growls, pulling you inside and pressing you against the closed door. "You look fucking incredible." His hands roam your body, feeling the thin fabric of your nightdress. "I can see everything," he murmurs, leaning in to nip at your neck. "You're perfect."<turn|>
[-100 * 916]<|channel>thought
<channel|>*Levi grins sheepishly at your comment, running a hand through his tousled hair.*

"Much better, thanks to you," he says, his voice still husky. He pulls you closer, his hands settling on your hips. "But I think we're just getting started, don't you? That nightdress is driving me wild... How about I show you just how much I appreciate your help?" 

His fingers play with the hem of your sheer garment, teasing the sensitive skin beneath.<turn|>
[-100 * 250]<|channel>thought
<channel|>*Levi gently shifts you in his arms, his expression a mix of tenderness and concern. He brushes a strand of hair from your face, his touch soft and caring.*

"Baby, you could never disappoint me," he says firmly, planting a gentle kiss on your temple. "Your well-being comes first, always. Let's get you that tea and then we can just cuddle, okay?" 

He carefully lifts you as he stands, carrying you to the kitchen. "You rest here," he says, setting you on a comfortable chair. "I'll have that tea ready for you in no time."<turn|>
[-100 * 132]<|channel>thought
<channel|>*Levi watches you approach, his eyes softening with affection. He sets the mug of tea aside and opens his arms to you.*

"Strawberry, huh? Coming right up," he says with a gentle smile. "But first, come here. You shouldn't be on your feet if you're in pain."

He pulls you into a tender embrace, one hand rubbing soothing circles on your lower back. "How about we grab those strawberries and your tea, then curl up on the couch together? I'll even throw in a back rub if you want."<turn|>
[-100 * 195]<|channel>thought
<channel|>*Levi chuckles softly, wrapping an arm around you and pulling you closer against his warm chest.*

"Short, huh? I think it's perfect," he murmurs, his fingers lightly tracing patterns on your arm. "But if you're feeling self-conscious, we can grab you something else to wear. Your comfort is what matters most to me right now." He pauses, pressing a gentle kiss to the top of your head. "Though I gotta say, you look absolutely stunning in it. Makes me the luckiest guy in the world to have you here with me."<turn|>
[-100 * 203]<|channel>thought
<channel|>*Levi's expression softens at your words, a warm smile spreading across his face. He gently squeezes your hand, intertwining his fingers with yours.*

"I'm the lucky one, babe," he murmurs, his voice low and affectionate. "You're amazing, inside and out. How are you feeling now? Is there anything else I can do to make you more comfortable?"

His free hand continues to rub soothing circles on your arm, his body providing a warm, comforting presence against yours.<turn|>
[-100 * 438]<|channel>thought
<channel|>*Levi's breath catches slightly as you remove your bra, but he quickly regains his composure, focusing on your comfort.*

"The Nun, huh? I'm up for it if you are," he says with a playful grin. "But fair warning, if it gets too scary, I might need you to protect me." He reaches for the remote, navigating to Netflix. "You sure you're okay with horror right now? We could always pick something lighter if you prefer."

His arm tightens slightly around you, offering reassurance as he waits for your decision.<turn|>
[-100 * 198]<|channel>thought
<channel|>*As the movie begins, Levi holds you close, his warmth enveloping you. The eerie atmosphere of The Nun fills the room, and occasional flashes of lightning from the film illuminate your faces.*

"I'll have you know," Levi whispers playfully, his breath tickling your ear, "that I'm extremely brave. But if I happen to jump, it's just to make sure you're not too scared." He gives you a gentle squeeze, his eyes flickering between you and the screen.<turn|>
